message.body: Yessssss!!!! I went to look at dresses to see if there was anything for you for your bday, and they completely got rid of the dresses category. So then I snooped on Google and it says they've stopped. They want to focus on undergarments and perfumes. No more clothes!
I know! I'm so pissed! Needless to say, my angel credit card will be used a lot less now.
I'm looked at AT&T to see how much a new phone is...an iPhone 6 is still like $450 after a contract upgrade? That's mad ridiculous.
I got a 89 on my micro exam!!! :D

I was up until 1 in the morning working on these damn graphs...I didn't even finish the respiration rate one. I emailed my lab partner to see if he knew what to do. If he doesn't, I'll ask adam during lab.
I was able to make the first graph have the x axis as time, y axis as optical density, and (somehow) got the lines to represent all 4 temperatures for ecoli.
Do you mind if I send it to you so you can proof read my question 3? It was about interpreting the graph and I don't know if what I said makes sense...cause I did it so late.
You can send it. I'll try to read it when I get a sec. It's a little busy
